==English==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[δαιμονίζομαι]]''' (''daemonizomai'') "to be possessed by a demon", from '''[[δαίμων]]''' (''deamon'') "[[demon]]".

===Intransitive verb===
'''daemonize'''
#(''of a computer program or script'') to prepare to go in to the background and become a [[daemon]]

